body:
**Description**

I am using SkiaSharp library to reduce the image brightness and it works properly in the older SkiaSharp version [1.59.3] and I am currently upgrading the SKiaSharp version to 2.80.0. I am trying to reduce the image brightness in the higher version but it doesn't look great. Kindly provide any suggestion to resolve this issue. 

**Code**

```csharp
            using (Stream destination = new FileStream("dest_image.png", FileMode.OpenOrCreate, FileAccess.ReadWrite))
            {
                Stream source = new FileStream(@"source.png", FileMode.OpenOrCreate, FileAccess.ReadWrite);
                SKBitmap bitmap = new SKBitmap(1, 1);
                bitmap = SKBitmap.Decode(source);
                float correctionFactor = 0.80f;
                //Reduce the picture color brightness
                for (int i = 0; i < bitmap.Width; i++)
                {
                    for (int j = 0; j < bitmap.Height; j++)
                    {
                        SKColor color = bitmap.GetPixel(i, j);
                        float red = (float)color.Red;
                        float green = (float)color.Green;
                        float blue = (float)color.Blue;
                        red = (255 - red) * correctionFactor + red;
                        green = (255 - green) * correctionFactor + green;
                        blue = (255 - blue) * correctionFactor + blue;
                        bitmap.SetPixel(i, j, new SKColor((byte)red, (byte)green, (byte)blue, color.Alpha));
                    }
                }
                Stream temp = SKImage.FromBitmap(bitmap).Encode(SKEncodedImageFormat.Png, 100).AsStream();
                temp.CopyTo(destination);
            }
```

**Source Image:**
![source](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/48026813/88921405-19e65000-d28c-11ea-8fbc-7858121056b1.png)

**Expected Behavior**

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/48026813/88921445-2ec2e380-d28c-11ea-9af9-76602b7a42a1.png)


**Actual Behavior**

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/48026813/88921500-44d0a400-d28c-11ea-929f-e1c09f961536.png)

**Basic Information**

- Version with issue:  2.80.0
- Last known good version:  1.59.3
- IDE:   Visual Studio 2017
- Platform Target Frameworks: .NET Core 2.1
